{"tid":749993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ACG毒撚末日] CCTV點名B站：有涉兄妹戀的亂倫內容；要製作傳播正能量鮮明的青少年節目","createTime":"2018-07-20T13:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T02:49:43.000Z","uid":67294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e412fb40bb9a9428e93ad41edb6c25f77ef65e4","tid":749993,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/catchpic/7/75/7510c997d8f77ce9b1853f9cc7336070.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Fcatchpic%2F7%2F75%2F7510c997d8f77ce9b1853f9cc7336070.png%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=5f0343c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/catchpic/8/8e/8e470a248141de9b2c37a3521d1b7bd9.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Fcatchpic%2F8%2F8e%2F8e470a248141de9b2c37a3521d1b7bd9.png%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=762a2c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7月20日消息，央視新聞頻道點名批評了B站以及其他網站、APP的低俗動漫內容，稱有一些動漫甚至涉及&ldquo;兄妹戀&rdquo;等亂倫內容。<br />\n<br />\n在央視的這篇報導中提到，網絡動漫作品中充斥著大量令人擔憂的低俗內容，而在B站能夠搜到不少類似&ldquo;穿著暴露的少女、曖昧的語言和動作&rdquo;內容的動漫作品，甚至有些涉及兄妹戀等，而部分內容還能作為編輯推薦出現，不少網友評論道，這樣的內容是如何過審？但平台方並沒有回應網友的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n除了B站，央視報導中還提到了幾個最受00後歡迎的漫畫app，在這些app中也可以搜到充斥著低俗畫面和情節的漫畫作品，另外這種現象也出現在不少動漫公眾號的推送文章和COS中。<br />\n<br />\nB站方面尚未就此次央視報導作出回應。"},{"pid":"1d91a0709145d9352dc5a7cd056ed24c26b17625","tid":749993,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70f11ac13aef52accebfd9099f5d2a274f30227f","tid":749993,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae963989b3ca85186ea322bc9ea28e8f00858f5","tid":749993,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"動漫內容低俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e49f89833ea247dc90a71001336b3eb248dfb7","tid":749993,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"閪羊羊夠宣揚虐畜思想啦<br />\n快撚啲取締佢啦"},{"pid":"87c74ed81dab99e26801bbf8fc608ee5df10804c","tid":749993,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"啲官有錢佬玩海天盛宴乜都得<br />\n毒撚想打個J都俾人禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9133773595379d673a1223da9c7efb7752ad7200","tid":749993,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}